reduce() Kya Hai?

Simple definition:

Stream ke saare elements ko combine karke ek hi final value banana.

Visual:

1 2 3 4 5
      ↓
reduce()
      ↓
15

Yahan:

Input = 5 elements
Output = 1 element
Real Life Example

Tumhare paas shopping bill hai.

100
200
300
400

Final Bill kitna hua?

100 + 200 + 300 + 400

↓

1000

Yehi reduce hai.